---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Trace Viewer — ponens">
  <section class="page-head">
    <h1>Trace Viewer</h1>
    <p>The interactive visualizer — flow, lineage, the artifact DAG, the reasoning funnel, the
      policies dashboard, and the <strong>residual surface</strong>. Below is the Stripe payment-flow
      example (a re-capture bug found and proved, 14 properties proven, plus its declared gaps).
      Locally, run <code>ponens trace view &lt;file&gt;</code> on any trace.</p>
  </section>
  <div class="viewer-frame">
    <iframe src="/viewer/visualizer.html" title="ponens trace viewer" loading="lazy"></iframe>
  </div>
  <p class="viewer-note">
    Open the example full-screen: <a href="/viewer/visualizer.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">/viewer/visualizer.html ↗</a>
  </p>
</Layout>
